    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS service. The chassis remains taut with refreshed suspension components, maintaining the platform\u2019s signature 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. A turn-key performance icon for the discerning driver.",
