    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and value, having been maintained with a clear focus on mechanical longevity. The exterior finish presents beautifully with a deep shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a light scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has remained a strictly smoke-free environment; the leather seating remains soft and supportive with only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is dry and responsive, benefiting from a recent professional oil service and a cooling system flush. The brakes feel firm, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle that drives straight and true, offering a premium experience for its next owner. Full service records are available for review.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
