      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, which offers a superior balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously inspected by our senior technicians to ensure total mechanical integrity, this model exemplifies the high standards of our curated inventory. It remains in commendable condition, representing a premier opportunity for the driver who demands both a refined aesthetic and proven reliability. This vehicle stands as a testament to diligent ownership and is prepared for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been so well-loved and is still in really solid shape, perfect for your daily commute or weekend getaways! It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken great care of it over the years, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
