      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing the platform's primary structural Achilles heel\u2014and a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The drivetrain is anchored by the factory M-Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional traction through the corners. Maintenance is up to date, including a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the chassis dynamics remain tight thanks to refreshed control arm bushings and a precise steering rack. This is a driver-spec machine engineered for those who value mechanical transparency and the visceral feedback of a naturally aspirated 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 31500.0,
